# LoTN V5 data

Canonical game data: `wod_chargen/games/lotn_v5/data/*.json` — not inline in `app/`.

Archetype weights: edit `data/archetype_themes.json`, run `scripts/apply_archetype_themes.py`, validate with `scripts/validate_archetype_biases.py`. See `docs/archetype-weight-guidelines.md`.

After adding packaged JSON/Python: `python scripts/generate_pyscript_config.py`.
